{"tid":2236563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞咗個有關過去一年香港社運嘅藝術展《粉飾太平》","createTime":"2020-10-09T14:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T15:40:29.000Z","uid":143257,"like":286,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ec94322760d1fd3d4773a694de0a34d56a4886","tid":2236563,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"唔知大家仲有冇印象喺半年前有《粉飾太平》嘅出現，期後喺連登得到大家支持，好多市民用咗自己方法黎繼續進行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f7whrU3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7whrU3.png&h=5dc8892a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1wpVX5h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wpVX5h.jpg&h=ddca057a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太古市民<br />\n<br />\n最近深水埗大南街parallel space搵小弟想擺一個關於呢年幾嘅作品展，主要都係關於運動同社會。<br />\n（parallel space 係深水埗大南街一個展覽場地，我都知連登上個禮拜先插緊大南街周圍coffee shop同發展商問題，不過parallel space係兩層都純粹for 展覽嘅地方，佢哋搵我，我難得有機會擺到呢類作品，我緊係嘍飯應啦！）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然入面仲有展出小弟其他作品，都係關於運動、社會、監控、傳媒、香港同中國等方向。<br />\n<br />\n例如：用五幅世界地圖撕貼出香港地圖，其實呢個作品係當時國安法一立，我所做嘅作品。當有國家幫香港出聲，中國就話「不得干預國家內政」，但其實香港本身就係一個國際性城市，並唔係單單屬於中國⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ET5qATY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FET5qATY.jpg&h=fe1e288d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zs5eudZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZs5eudZ.jpg&h=dfbcbf80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，仲有件係互動作品，係比入場觀眾自行貼上膠紙，因為係《粉飾太平》時，好多人問「貼膠紙怕唔怕犯法」，但我覺得如果連咁少事我哋都要怕，之後只會越黎越多嘢唔敢做。<br />\nDay1<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DB3vM5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDB3vM5c.jpg&h=f4dc3a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDay5<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUdLAYy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUdLAYy.jpg&h=91ac029f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDay8<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XBH8yLf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBH8yLf.jpg&h=1c85d9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好幾件其他作品，但我廢事咁長文，有興趣嘅既巴打歡迎follow 小弟ig (@gllh_art)，多多支持小弟可以繼續以藝術方式回應社會。<br />\n<br />\n最後希望各位巴絲多多支持！<br />\n<br />\n展覽日期：10月1日至10月18日（有機會延長至24-25號）<br />\n時間：每天中午 12:00 至 晚上 07:00（逢星期一休息）<br />\n地點 / Venue : Parallel Space <br />\n地址／Address :G/F, 202, Tai Nan Street, Sham Shui Po / 深水埗大南街202號<br />\n<br />\n費用：免費（場內有售明信片，希望大家支持下小弟創作同 parallel space）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟ig : gllh_art <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgllh_art%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=6ab5b6d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/</a><br />\nParallel space ig: parallel_space_hk <br />\n<br />\n反思現今社會狀況係咪正常（半年前嘅post)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1898726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1898726</a>"},{"pid":"e0ef27d58d1894b291bd9475b6eeaa11dacf11d4","tid":2236563,"uid":143257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:28:39.000Z","msg":"黎咗嘅巴絲，係到留個言傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未黎嘅都留吓，推下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係現場認到我，撞到黎say個hi"},{"pid":"06a9d6eec874f7c2c9c78aac1d12e4df68b7aa43","tid":2236563,"uid":204466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"支持延長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c97a200f4939ef699ad40f5c67eb14f54b0e02","tid":2236563,"uid":95445,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:32:29.000Z","msg":"巴打好耐冇玩銀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會搵事頭婆銀仔砌返幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\"